## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c0237-102">때는 <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D> 개체에 할당 된 <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationProcessor2D.Pivot%2A> 속성의는 <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationProcessor2D> 개체는 요소가 단일 조작자에 의해 조작 될 때 조작 프로세서는 요소를 회전 변경을 계산 하는 방법에 영향을 줍니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c0237-102">When a <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D> object is assigned to the <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationProcessor2D.Pivot%2A> property of a <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationProcessor2D> object, it affects how the manipulation processor calculates rotational changes to an element when the element is being manipulated by a single manipulator.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c0237-103">조작 하는 동안 둘 이상의 조작자 요소에 적용 되는지, 피벗 속성은 무시 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c0237-103">If more than one manipulator is being applied to the element during manipulation, the Pivot property is ignored.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c0237-104">단일 조작자 시나리오에서는 요소를 끌 때 회전할 수 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c0237-104">In a single-manipulator scenario, an element can rotate as it is being dragged.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c0237-105"><xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.X%2A> 및 <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.Y%2A> 의 속성은 <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D> , 주위로 회전 하는 요소는 위치를 결정 하는 개체 및 <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.Radius%2A> 속성은 회전 변경 횟수를 계산 조작 프로세서에서 사용 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c0237-105">The <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.X%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.Y%2A> properties of the <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D> object determine what position the element rotates around, and the <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.Radius%2A> property is used by the manipulation processor to calculate the amount of rotational change.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c0237-106">예를 들어, 단일 조작자에 가까운 경우 피벗 점의 바깥쪽 가장자리 요소 회전 변경은 끌 됩니다 상당히 많은 (요소의 크기에 따라).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c0237-106">For instance, if the single manipulator is near the outer edge of the pivot point, the rotational change to the element as it is being dragged will be fairly large (depending upon the size of the element).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c0237-107">조작 자가 있는 경우 피벗 점의 가운데 (있는 경우)에 매우 적은 회전만 발생 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c0237-107">If the manipulator is close to the center of the pivot point, very little (if any) rotation will occur.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c0237-108">일반적으로 <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.X%2A> 및 <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.Y%2A> 속성 나타냅니다 조작 되 고 요소 중심 및 <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.Radius%2A> 속성 가장 먼 가장자리를 요소 중심에서 까지의 거리를 나타냅니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c0237-108">Typically, the <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.X%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.Y%2A> properties represent the center of the element that is being manipulated, and the <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.Radius%2A> property represents the distance from the center of the element to its farthest edge.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c0237-109">요소를 이동할 때는 <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.X%2A> 및 <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.Y%2A> 의 속성은 <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D> 회전이 발생할 때 적절 한 지점에 계속 되도록 업데이트 해야 하는 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c0237-109">As the element moves, the <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.X%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.Y%2A> properties of the <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D> object need to be updated so that rotation will continue to occur around the proper point.</span></span>  
  
   
  
